quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  14,10,"NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en maaki: \"E hara sikke no e fii Alla, fuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, himo nodda on fii yo O haforan on yoga e junuubi mon, himo nennana on haa e lajal innaangal?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"On wonaali si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru amen. HiЙ—on faandii nde sakkotoЙ—on(falotodon) men e kon ko baabiraaЙ“e amen rewaynoo. Addanee men hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  14,11,"NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en maakani Й“e: \"[Ko goonga], men wonaali si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru mon, kono Alla no moЖҙЖҙoo e Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Laatanaaki men nde men addana on hujja, si wanaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Ko e Alla gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotoo"
  14,12,"Ko haЙ—ata men nde fawotoo e Alla, gomЙ—ii O fewnii men (e) laawi amen? Ma men muГұГұo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotoo"
  14,13,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e (kadi) wi'ani NulaaЙ“e mun Й“en: \"Ma men yaltin on ka leydi amen, maa ruttoЙ—on e diina amen\". Joomi maЙ“Й“e wahayini e maЙ“Й“e: \"Ma men halku tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  14,14,"Ma Men hoЙ—nu on e leydi ndin Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. ЖҠum ko wonannde on huluЙ—o daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa Am on"
  14,15,ЖҒe Й—aЙ“Й“i uddital. Sooyi kala dunndaranke ЖҙagguЙ—o
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ЖҙiiЖҙiiri"
  14,17,"himo wooЙ“a Й—am, e Й—eЙ“ataa Й“ennugol Й—am. Maayde nden ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaali maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte sattuЙ—e"
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa Й“en yedduЙ“e Joomi mun, kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tiiЙ—i e mun, e Гұalaande wippoore. ЖҒe hettoytaa huunde e ko Й“e faggitinoo. Ko Й—um woni majjere wonЙ—Й—unde"
  14,19,"E a yi'aali Alla tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin goonga? Si O muuyii, O ittay on O adda tagu hesu"
  14,20,Й—um wonaali sattuЙ—um ka Alla
  14,21,"ЖҒe feeГұana Alla Й“e denndaangal. Lo'uЙ“e Й“en wi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Menen men wonanno on jokkuЙ“e. Taw si on duncanay men e lepte Alla Й—en goЙ—Й—um?\" ЖҒen wi'a: \"Sinno Alla fewnuno men, men fewnayno on. Hino fota e amen, si en Й—enЖҙi maa si en muГұГұi; daЙ—irde alanaa en"
  14,22,"Seytaane wi'a, tuma fiyaaku on Гұaawaa: \"Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga; mi fodi on mi lunndii on. Alanaa lam e mo'on immorde e hujja, si wanaa mi nodii on, on jaabike lam. Wata on felam; felee ko'e mon. Wanaa mi faabotooЙ—o on; wanaa on faabotooЙ“e lam. Mi yeddii ko kafidunoЙ—on mi kon [e Alla] ado (hannde)\". Pellet, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  14,23,"GomЙ—imЙ“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й“en naatnaa e Aljannaaji, canЙ—i hino ila ley majji, ko Й“e duumorayЙ“e ton e duЕӢayee Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Hiwraandu maЙ“Й“e ndun ton ko: \"Salaam\" (Kisiyee). @Corrected"
  14,24,"E a yi'aali ko honno Alla piyiri misal konngol laaЙ“ungol, ko wano leggal welngal, binndeere maggal ko tabituЙ—i, calЙ—i maggal no ka weeyo"
  14,25,"Hingal okkira dimЙ—e maggal on tuma kala, e duЕӢayee Joomi maggal. Alla no piyana yimЙ“e Й“en mise, belajo'o Й“e waajitoto"
  14,26,"Ko woni kadi misal konngol soЙ“ungol, ko wano leggal soЙ“ungal, irtaangal ka hoore-leydi, ngal alanaa Й—um ГұiiЙ“irde"
  14,27,"Alla no tabintinira gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en konngol tabitungol, ka nguurandam aduna e ka laakara. Alla no majjina tooГұooЙ“e Й“en. Alla no waЙ—a ko O muuyi"